---
description: TS, UI, quality bar
alwaysApply: true
---

# Core

- **TS**: no semicolons; `interface` > `type` for shapes; no `any` (`unknown` + guards); destructure
- **Style**: functional bias (`map`/`filter`/`reduce`); side effects at edges
- **UI**: Tailwind only (no inline `style` except animation); `cn`/`clsx` for long classes
- **Names**: English camelCase / PascalCase / UPPER_SNAKE; no Japanese identifiers
- **Comments**: JSDoc on exported APIs only
- **Debug**: no committed `console.log`; `// DEBUG:` local only
- **Tests**: Vitest; `*.test.ts` / `*.spec.ts` colocated
- **Secrets**: env only; never commit `.env*`
